######
# employee-server
######

### 获取所有员工信息
GET http://localhost:9999/employees HTTP/1.1


### 注册新员工
POST http://localhost:9999/employees HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "id": 1,
    "name": "name1",
    "department": "d1"
}


### 根据 name 查询员工信息
POST http://localhost:9999/getemployeebyname HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "id": -1,
    "name": "name1",
    "department": ""
}


### 根据 id工号 查询员工信息
POST http://localhost:9999/getemployeebyid HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "id": 1,
    "name": "",
    "department": ""
}


### 更新员工信息，以 id工号 为标识
POST http://localhost:9999/editemployee HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "id": 1,
    "name": "newname1",
    "department": "newdepartment"
}



