######
# task-server
######

### 获取所有任务信息
GET http://localhost:9997/tasks HTTP/1.1

### 获取一个用户的是所有任务
POST http://localhost:9997/gettasksbyuserid HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "taskid":-10,
    "userid":1,
    "category":-10,
    "completed":true
}

### 根据 category 获取某一类任务
POST http://localhost:9997/gettasksbycategory HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "taskid":-10,
    "userid":-10,
    "category":1,
    "completed":true
}

### 根据 工号 和 category 获取某些任务
POST http://localhost:9997/gettasksbyuseridandcategory HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "taskid":-10,
    "userid":1,
    "category":1,
    "completed":true
}

### 测试用，手动添加任务
POST http://localhost:9997/test1 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "taskid":100,
    "userid":100,
    "category":1,
    "completed":true
}


